---
title: Smart Moo Shu-Sesame Beyond Meat® Patties with Crisp Salad and Tahini Drizzle
description: Lightly sweetened, deeply savoury and bolstered by the sweetness of grated apple as well as a zippy Moo Shu spice blend, these Beyond Meat® patties will be enjoyed by everyone in your family.

